<dialog
  id="search-modal"
  class="modal modal-bottom sm:modal-middle"
  aria-label="Cerca nel sito Aquaura"
>
  <div class="modal-box bg-base-100 backdrop-blur-xl border border-base-content/10 shadow-2xl">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-base-content/60 flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 text-primary"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 21l-5.197-5.197m0 0A7.5 7.5 0 105.196 5.196a7.5 7.5 0 0010.607 10.607z" /></svg>
        Cerca nel sito
      </h2>
      <button
        type="button"
        class="btn btn-ghost btn-xs text-base-content/40 hover:text-base-content"
        aria-label="Chiudi ricerca"
        onclick="this.closest('dialog')?.close();"
      >
        ✕
      </button>
    </div>

    <form method="dialog" class="space-y-4">
      <label class="form-control w-full">
        <span class="label-text text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-base-content/40 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
          Termine di ricerca
        </span>
        <div class="relative group">
          <input
            type="search"
            name="q"
            placeholder="Cerca contenuti, servizi, articoli..."
            class="input input-bordered w-full bg-base-100/80 border-base-content/10 focus:border-primary focus:outline-none pl-11 h-12"
            autofocus
          >
          <div class="absolute left-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-base-content/20 group-focus-within:text-primary transition-colors">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 21l-5.197-5.197m0 0A7.5 7.5 0 105.196 5.196a7.5 7.5 0 0010.607 10.607z" /></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </label>

      <p class="text-[0.7rem] text-base-content/40 leading-relaxed">
        Questa è una ricerca di base lato interfaccia. Puoi perfezionarla o collegarla in futuro ad un motore di ricerca interno.
      </p>

      <div class="modal-action">
        <button
          type="submit"
          class="btn btn-primary btn-sm rounded-full px-6 text-[0.75rem] uppercase tracking-[0.18em]"
        >
          Chiudi
        </button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
</dialog>

